% B6 -- baseline raiseerror -> stop round-trip.
% Each iteration: raiseerror populates $errordict (incl. stack
% snapshots if recordstacks=true), pushes /cmd onto ostack and
% stop onto estack; dispatcher runs stop, walks estack to the
% stopped marker, unwinds; stopped pushes true; handleerror
% consumes /cmd via print_error and resets newerror.
% recordstacks defaults to true after sli-init runs init_errordict.
tic 1000000 { { /test /Bench raiseerror } stopped { handleerror } if } repeat toc ==
quit
